metadata.name: Stella
metadata.description:
First of creation.

A stellar flash from the darkness.

Nothing then something.

A dense ball of nothingness with gravity to pull you towards its centre.


Note: Each one of these 1/1 NFTs comes with a high-resolution digital image for personal use and a unique signed print shipped to the winner of the original auction (please contact me and include a shipping address in case you'd like to receive the print
